effect.shortEffect: Changes the bearer's type to match each move it uses.
effect.full: Changes the bearer's type to match each move it uses. The type change takes place just before the move is used.

description.x-y: Changes the Pokémon’s type to the type of the move it’s using.
description.omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire: Changes the Pokémon’s type to the type of the move it’s using.
description.sun-moon: Changes the Pokémon’s type to the type of the move it’s about to use.
description.ultra-sun-ultra-moon: Changes the Pokémon’s type to the type of the move it’s about to use.
description.lets-go-pikachu-lets-go-eevee: Changes the Pokémon’s type to the type of the move it’s about to use.
